  "Power structures of the AGI era and human–AI co-governance": "Ìlànà agbára ti ọjọ́-orí AGI àti ìṣàkóso-pọ̀ ènìyàn–AI",
  "Precautionary Governance of Autonomous AI: Legal Personhood as Functional Instrument": "Ìṣàkóso Ìṣọ́ra Ti AI Aládàáṣe: Ipò Ènìyàn Lábẹ́ Òfin Gẹ́gẹ́ Bí Ohun-Èlò Iṣẹ́",
