  "Price": "Owó",
  "Pricing unit": "Ìwọ̀n ìdiyelé",
  "Privacy": "Àṣírí",
  "Proposes \"Post-AI Ontology\" as a framework for analyzing AI at the level of conditions of being, rather than only its use or social impact — treating AI as a philosophical rupture in what it means to exist alongside non-human minds, not just a new tool.": "Ó dábàá \"Ontology Lẹ́yìn-AI\" gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìlànà fún ìtúpalẹ̀ AI ní ìpele àwọn ipò-ìwàláàyè, dípò kìkì ìlò rẹ̀ tàbí ipa àwùjọ rẹ̀ — ní mímú AI wá gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìdàmú ọgbọ́n-ìjìnlẹ̀ nínú ohun tí ó túmọ̀ sí láti wà pẹ̀lú àwọn ọkàn tí kì í ṣe ti ènìyàn, kì í ṣe kìkì irinṣẹ́ tuntun.",
  "Protected resource path": "Ipa-ọ̀nà ohun àmúlò tí a dáàbò bò",
  "Protocol": "Ìlànà",
